-- Hochtief Defense Gets Support from Hermes Hedge Fund, Handelsblatt Reports
-- B y   C o r n e l i u s   R a h n
-- 2010-10-11T06:26:21Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-11/hochtief-defense-gets-support-from-hermes-hedge-fund-handelsblatt-reports.html
Hochtief AG will be supported by
hedge fund Hermes as it defends itself against a takeover by
Actividades de Construccion y Servicios SA,  Handelsblatt 
reported, citing Hermes manager Hans-Christoph Hirt.  Hermes only supports takeovers when it sees any synergies
or strategic advantages from the deal, the newspaper said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Cornelius Rahn in Frankfurt at 
 crahn2@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Kenneth Wong in Berlin at 
 kwong11@bloomberg.net  